Why it’s the same “apathy” role

Because the triangle isn’t about specific emotions—it’s about engagement structure:

State	Energy	Direction	Function
Courage	High	Toward	Act despite risk
Fear	High	Away	Avoid threat
Apathy	Low	None	No movement

👉 So:

Apathy is the zero-state for any high-energy polarity

